        "created_at": "2019-07-17T05:41:02.794Z",
        "cooked": "<p>After looking through the docs, could this be achieved by setting the same <code>locality_machineid</code> parameter in each DC?</p>\n<p>EDIT: I\u2019ve found <code>locality_zoneid</code>. Is this what I should be using?</p>",
